Pandas missing
================

<!-- WARNING: THIS FILE WAS AUTOGENERATED! DO NOT EDIT! -->

## Install

`pip install pandas-missing`

## How to use

``` python
import pandas as pd
import pandas_missing.Missing

from pandas_missing import *
```

``` python
df = pd.DataFrame.from_dict(
    {
        "number": range(0, 15)
    }
)

df.iloc[3:6, :] = None

df
```
